---
title: Beef Steak & Zingy Cherry Tomato Salad with Lime & Sweet Chilli Dressing
description: Juicy beef rump steak meets its match with a fresh green salad, all tied together with a sweet and zesty dressing. It’s the perfect balance of bold flavours and crisp, refreshing bites—simple, satisfying, and seriously delicious!

